    <p>MP, MS, JB and RWA conceived of the study and participated in the coordination of the project. MP, MS, JB and RWA participated in the design of the database and the web interface. All authors were involved in algorithm development. MB and SW implemented the search algorithms for small structural elements. MP, MS, MB and RWA contributed to analyse the results. MP, MS, EKB and RWA drafted the manuscript. All authors read and approved of the final draft.</p>
